narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: The Nemours Foundation is a General Acute Care Hospital  Children provider based in Orlando, FL. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $105.0M in Medicaid payments across 644K claims serving 0 beneficiaries.

narrative.text: This provider received $105.0M in taxpayer-funded Medicaid payments — enough to fund healthcare for approximately 13,118 Medicaid beneficiaries for a full year at average per-enrollee costs.
